CMS::Joomla
===========

This module provides an interface for reading Joomla! CMS configuration
variables and connecting to the Joomla! database from Perl script.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc CMS::Joomla

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN:
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/CMS-Joomla

    Example programs:
        http://dist.epipe.com/joomla/perl/


